<h2 id="Syntax">Syntax</h2>

<pre class="twopartsyntaxbox"><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax" title="CSS/Value_definition_syntax">Formal syntax</a>: <code><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/left" title="&lt;length&gt; | &lt;percentage&gt; | auto">&lt;'left'&gt;</a></code>
</pre>

<pre>offset-block-start: 3px         /* &lt;length&gt; values */
offset-block-start: 2.4em

offset-block-start: 10%         /* &lt;percentage&gt;s of the width or height of the containing block */

offset-block-start: auto

offset-block-start: inherit</pre>

<h3 id="Values">Values</h3>

<p>The <code>offset-block-start</code> property takes the same values as the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/left" title="The left CSS property specifies part of the position of positioned elements."><code>left</code></a> property.</p>